title: Dita Von Teese
summary: Heather Ren√©e Sweet (born September 28, 1972), known professionally as Dita Von Teese, is an American vedette, burlesque dancer, model, fashion designer, businesswoman, and author.[1] She is credited with re-popularizing burlesque performance, earning the moniker "Queen of Burlesque".[2][3][4][5]
